<p class="contenttext"><b>Group Rules:</b></p>
<p class="contenttext"><b>Sequential:  </b>This is a procedure how the calls will be assigned to the employees in that group. Sequential rule means the calls will be connected to the employees which we will create one by one.</p>

<p class="contenttext"><b>Weighted: </b>In this rule calls will be assigned to the employees based on the “Employee weight” entered in the Add employee to Group form.</p>
If the list of employees are having same weight number means, those all comes under one level, and sequential method will apply here.</p>

<p class="contenttext"><b>Action perform on Connect:</b> You can provide API for us to call as soon as call connect happens in this group. This can be used to integrate with 3rd party application and provide data in realtime.</p>

